_json.description: Balcony BBQ - "Are you used to going to the park to enjoy a barbeque? There is no need any more! After the success of the notebook BBQ we now laso offer balcony barbeque. It is ideal if you do not have a lot of space, live in a student house or do not have a garden. Moreover this BBQ hangs on the perfect height, so you do have to bend down to check that your meat hasn't burned. Balcony BBQ hangs on the inside of the balcony. Simple deisgn makes it really easy to maintain."
